    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The faculty of the college is very good. Well experienced and knowledge teachers are there",
          "name": "Nishu Kumari",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Infrastructure and facilities like labs, library, academic auditoriums, etc.",
          "name": "Siddhant Jain",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The things I liked were the cooperative environment in the college along with supportive faculty.",
          "name": "Siddhant Jain",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Teaching staff is very qualified and supporting in every subject",
          "name": "Mohit Yadav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Fests and Seminars are held regularly for the overall growth of students",
          "name": "Mohit Yadav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "KMC is one of the most reputed colleges in Delhi University for commerce with very good placement and internship opportunities",
          "name": "Mohit Yadav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like the course curriculum and its actually a broad way to give us wide knowledge.",
          "name": "Ashutosh Prasad",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like the ambience and infrastructure of my college, it's one of the heritage building of Delhi University.",
          "name": "Ashutosh Prasad",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like the location of my college, especially the North campus.",
          "name": "Ashutosh Prasad",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "i like the faculty of my course the best. the faculty of my course is really helpful and puts a lot of efforts to make education more interacting .",
          "name": "Jasmin",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Infrastructure of college should be more good, the capacity of room.is very small",
          "name": "Nishu Kumari",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Not much focus on extracurriculars in the college and no attention in incrementing skills of students.",
          "name": "Siddhant Jain",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Lack of sports facilities for students playing the sports like Lawn Tennis.",
          "name": "Siddhant Jain",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Sports facilities are also not upto the mark. I am a basketball enthusiast but there is no court for basketball.Cricket facilities are also not good.",
          "name": "Mohit Yadav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The one this that our college is lacking is an auditorium.The work is under progress but it will be taking a lot of time in completition",
          "name": "Mohit Yadav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The campus is not as big as i expected it. The campus size is quite smaller than other colleges like Ramjas, St.Stephens etc",
          "name": "Mohit Yadav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "College has to work for the accessibility of cleaning the campus.",
          "name": "Ashutosh Prasad",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "the canteen food of my college does not have a variety of options. the quality of the food is hood but not a lot if varities are present",
          "name": "Jasmin",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "College administration has to focus on security measures.",
          "name": "Ashutosh Prasad",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "the infrastructure of this college is not that spacious. the building is nice but there is a need for more open space in the college.",
          "name": "Jasmin",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        }
      ]
    },
    "affiliated_to": {
      "name": "Delhi University, New Delhi"
    }
